item.title: About
item.description: I’m Will Stranathan, and I have a very small set of interests. Most of the content you’ll find on this site will be ramblings about football/soccer (usually Charlotte FC), or maybe software development. I live in Charlotte with my amazing wife. I’ve helped launch two adult humans to production, but they really did a lot of the work themselves.

item.title: Ahoy!
item.description: In 2022, one of the local football club blogs was having a video podcast, and in the live comments somebody on a mobile phone said “Westwood should ahoy more” which I assume was “shoot”. But “ahoy” stuck as a word we yell when somebody shoots from outside the box now.
